object.script:
function onTick() pitch_tilt = ((input.getNumber(10)*4)*90) roll_tilt = ((input.getNumber(11)*4)*90) top_tilt = input.getNumber(12) end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
pitch = math.acos(pitch_tilt / 180) roll = math.rad(90 - roll_tilt) troll = math.rad(0 - roll_tilt) broll = math.rad(180 - roll_tilt) croll = math.rad(90)
if top_tilt < 0 then roll = -roll end
radius = w+h roll_l_rad_t = (w+h)/5 roll_l_rad_b = roll_l_rad_t - 5 roll_t_rad_t = roll_l_rad_t - 10 roll_t_rad_b = roll_l_rad_t - 5
cx = w/2 cy = h/2
x1 = cx + radius * math.cos(roll + pitch) y1 = cy + radius * math.sin(roll + pitch) x2 = cx + radius * math.cos(roll - pitch) y2 = cy + radius * math.sin(roll - pitch)
if top_tilt < 0 then x3 = cx + radius * math.cos(-troll + pitch) y3 = cy + radius * math.sin(-troll + pitch)
x4 = cx + radius * math.cos(-broll + pitch) y4 = cy + radius * math.sin(-broll + pitch) else x3 = cx + radius * math.cos(broll + pitch) y3 = cy + radius * math.sin(broll + pitch)
x4 = cx + radius * math.cos(troll + pitch) y4 = cy + radius * math.sin(troll + pitch) end
--screen.setColor(50, 90, 151) -- blue --screen.drawTriangleF(x1, y1+1, x2, y2+1, x3, y3)
--screen.setColor(149, 74, 40) -- brown --screen.drawTriangleF(x1, y1+1, x2, y2+1, x4, y4)
screen.setColor(0, 80, 0, 250) -- white screen.drawLine(x1, y1, x2, y2)
screen.setColor(0, 80, 0, 250) -- yellow screen.drawLine(cx, cy+5, cx-5, cy) ---v--- screen.drawLine(cx, cy+5, cx+5, cy) screen.drawLine(cx, cy+6, cx-5, cy+1) ---v--- screen.drawLine(cx, cy+6, cx+5, cy+1)
screen.drawLine(cx-24, cy, cx-4, cy) ---v--- screen.drawLine(cx+5, cy, cx+25, cy) screen.drawLine(cx-24, cy+1, cx-4, cy+1) ---v--- screen.drawLine(cx+5, cy+1, cx+25, cy+1)
end

function round(num, numDecimalPlaces) local mult = 10^(numDecimalPlaces or 0) return math.floor(num * mult + 0.5) / mult end
function onTick() com = math.floor(input.getNumber(1)) alt = math.floor(input.getNumber(2)) spd = math.floor(input.getNumber(3)) target_alt = math.floor(input.getNumber(4)) bx = input.getNumber(5) target_spd = math.floor(input.getNumber(6)) spdx = input.getNumber(7)
com_tgl = input.getBool(10) alt_tgl = input.getBool(11) spd_tgl = input.getBool(12) alt_hld_toggle = input.getBool(13) spd_alt_ind= input.getBool(14) spd_hld_toggle = input.getBool(15) end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
if spd_alt_ind then screen.setColor(5, 5, 5, 120) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, w, 8) end
if spd_tgl then rspd = round(spd,-1) screen.setColor(5, 5, 5, 120) screen.drawRectF(0, (h/2)-18, 15, 35) screen.setColor(5, 5, 5) screen.drawRectF(0, (h/2)-5, 15, 8) screen.setColor(0, 80, 0, 250) screen.drawText(0, (h/2)-17, string.format("%#3d",rspd+20)) --speed 15pix screen.drawText(0, (h/2)-11, string.format("%#3d",rspd+10)) --speed 15pix screen.drawText(0, (h/2)-3, string.format("%#3d",spd)) --speed 15pix if spd > 10 then screen.drawText(0, (h/2)+5, string.format("%#3d",rspd-10)) --speed 15pix end if spd > 20 then screen.drawText(0, (h/2)+11, string.format("%#3d",rspd-20)) --speed 15pix end screen.setColor(0, 80, 0, 250) screen.drawRect(-1, (h/2)-5, 15, 8) end
if alt_tgl then
screen.setColor(5, 5, 5, 120) screen.drawRectF(w-20, (h/2)-18, 23, 35) screen.setColor(5, 5, 5) screen.drawRectF(w-20, (h/2)-5, 22, 8) screen.setColor(0, 80, 0, 250) ralt = round(alt,-2)
screen.drawText(w-19, (h/2)-17, string.format("%04d", ralt+200)) --alt 20 pix screen.drawText(w-19, (h/2)-11, string.format("%04d", ralt+100)) --alt 20 pix
if alt == target_alt and alt_hld_toggle then screen.setColor(0, 255, 255) --light blue screen.drawText(w-19, (h/2)-3, string.format("%04d", alt)) --alt 20 pix else screen.drawText(w-19, (h/2)-3, string.format("%04d", alt)) --alt 20 pix end
screen.setColor(0, 80, 0, 250) if alt > 100 then screen.drawText(w-19, (h/2)+5, string.format("%04d", ralt-100)) --alt 20 pix end
if alt > 200 then screen.drawText(w-19, (h/2)+11, string.format("%04d", ralt-200)) --alt 20 pix end
screen.setColor(0, 80, 0, 250) screen.drawRect(w-20, (h/2)-5, 22, 8)
if alt_hld_toggle then screen.setColor(0, 80, 0, 250) screen.drawText(w-20, 1, "ALHD") screen.setColor(0, 255, 255) --light blue screen.drawText(w-19, (h/2)-23, string.format("%04d", target_alt)) --alt 20 pix screen.drawTriangle(w-21, ((h/2)-15)+bx, w-21, ((h/2)-21)+bx, w-20, ((h/2)-18)+bx) end
if spd_hld_toggle then screen.setColor(0, 80, 0, 250) screen.drawText(1, 1, "SPHD") screen.setColor(0, 255, 255) --light blue screen.drawText(0, (h/2)-23, string.format("%03d", target_spd)) --alt 20 pix screen.drawTriangle(15, ((h/2)-15)+spdx, 15, ((h/2)-21)+spdx, 14, ((h/2)-18)+spdx) end
end
if com_tgl then screen.setColor(5, 5, 5) screen.drawRectF(w/2-9, -1, 17, 8) screen.setColor(0, 80, 0, 250) screen.drawText(w/2-7, 1, string.format("%03d",com)) --compass 15 pix screen.setColor(0, 80, 0, 250) screen.drawRect(w/2-9, -1, 17, 8) end end

function onTick() stall_speed = input.getNumber(1) cruise_speed = input.getNumber(2) max_speed = input.getNumber(3) spd = input.getNumber(4)
ss = (spd/stall_speed)*17 cs = (spd/cruise_speed)*17
end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
screen.setColor(200, 200, 0) --yellow screen.drawRectF(15, h/2+17, 2, -35)
screen.setColor(0, 200, 0) --green screen.drawRectF(15, h/2+17, 2, -35)
if ss < 33 then screen.setColor(200, 0, 0) --red screen.drawRectF(15, h/2+17, 2, -35+ss) end
end

function onTick() pitch_tilt = ((input.getNumber(10)*4)*90) roll_tilt = ((input.getNumber(11)*4)*90) end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
if roll_tilt > 45 then mroll_display = 45 else mroll_display = roll_tilt end if roll_tilt < -45 then mroll_display = -45 end
pitch = math.acos(pitch_tilt / 180) roll = math.rad(90 - roll_tilt) troll = math.rad(0 - roll_tilt) broll = math.rad(180 - roll_tilt) croll = math.rad(90)
fifthteen_roll_right = math.rad(75) fifthteen_roll_left = math.rad(105) thirty_roll_right = math.rad(60) thirty_roll_left = math.rad(120) fortyfive_roll_right = math.rad(45) fortyfive_roll_left = math.rad(135)
tlroll = math.rad(100 - mroll_display) trroll = math.rad(80 - mroll_display) tcroll = math.rad(90 - mroll_display)
radius = w+h roll_l_rad_t = (w+h)/7 -- bottom of the screen
roll_l_rad_b = roll_l_rad_t - 4 --top short line roll_t_rad_x = roll_l_rad_t - 6 --top long line roll_t_rad_c = roll_l_rad_t - 8 --top long line
roll_t_rad_t = roll_l_rad_t - 9 --top triangle roll_t_rad_b = roll_l_rad_t - 5 --bottom trianle
cx = w/2 cy = h/2+10
x11 = cx + roll_l_rad_t * math.cos(croll) --top line points 0 Degrees y11 = cy + roll_l_rad_t * math.sin(croll) x12 = cx + roll_t_rad_c * math.cos(croll) --bottom line points 0 Degrees y12 = cy + roll_t_rad_c * math.sin(croll)
x13 = cx + roll_l_rad_t * math.cos(thirty_roll_right) --top line points 30 Degrees y13 = cy + roll_l_rad_t * math.sin(thirty_roll_right) x14 = cx + roll_t_rad_x * math.cos(thirty_roll_right) --bottom line points 30 Degrees y14 = cy + roll_t_rad_x * math.sin(thirty_roll_right)
x15 = cx + roll_l_rad_t * math.cos(thirty_roll_left) --top line points 30 Degrees y15 = cy + roll_l_rad_t * math.sin(thirty_roll_left) x16 = cx + roll_t_rad_x * math.cos(thirty_roll_left) --bottom line points 30 Degrees y16 = cy + roll_t_rad_x * math.sin(thirty_roll_left)
x17 = cx + roll_l_rad_t * math.cos(fortyfive_roll_right) --top line points 45 Degrees y17 = cy + roll_l_rad_t * math.sin(fortyfive_roll_right) x18 = cx + roll_l_rad_b * math.cos(fortyfive_roll_right) --bottom line points 45 Degrees y18 = cy + roll_l_rad_b * math.sin(fortyfive_roll_right)
x19 = cx + roll_l_rad_t * math.cos(fortyfive_roll_left) --top line points 45 Degrees y19 = cy + roll_l_rad_t * math.sin(fortyfive_roll_left) x20 = cx + roll_l_rad_b * math.cos(fortyfive_roll_left) --bottom line points 45 Degrees y20 = cy + roll_l_rad_b * math.sin(fortyfive_roll_left)
x21 = cx + roll_l_rad_t * math.cos(fifthteen_roll_right) --top line points 15 Degrees y21 = cy + roll_l_rad_t * math.sin(fifthteen_roll_right) x22 = cx + roll_l_rad_b * math.cos(fifthteen_roll_right) --bottom line points 15 Degrees y22 = cy + roll_l_rad_b * math.sin(fifthteen_roll_right)
x23 = cx + roll_l_rad_t * math.cos(fifthteen_roll_left) --top line points 15 Degrees y23 = cy + roll_l_rad_t * math.sin(fifthteen_roll_left) x24 = cx + roll_l_rad_b * math.cos(fifthteen_roll_left) --bottom line points 15 Degrees y24 = cy + roll_l_rad_b * math.sin(fifthteen_roll_left)
x221 = cx + roll_t_rad_t * math.cos(tlroll) --triangle points y221 = cy + roll_t_rad_t * math.sin(tlroll) x222 = cx + roll_t_rad_t * math.cos(trroll) y222 = cy + roll_t_rad_t * math.sin(trroll) x223 = cx + roll_t_rad_b * math.cos(tcroll) y223 = cy + roll_t_rad_b * math.sin(tcroll)
screen.setColor(0, 80, 0, 250) -- white screen.drawLine(x11, y11, x12, y12) -- bottom line for roll screen.drawLine(x13, y13, x14, y14) screen.drawLine(x15, y15, x16, y16) screen.drawLine(x17, y17, x18, y18) screen.drawLine(x19, y19, x20, y20) screen.drawLine(x21, y21, x22, y22) screen.drawLine(x23, y23, x24, y24)
screen.setColor(0, 80, 0, 250) -- red screen.drawTriangleF(x221, y221, x222, y222, x223, y223)
end

object.script:
lsrX = 0 lsrY = 0 lsrZ = 0
function onTick()
lock = input.getBool(1) nvis = input.getBool(3) stab = input.getBool(2) laser = input.getBool(4)
lsrX = input.getNumber(10) lsrY = input.getNumber(11) lsrZ = input.getNumber(12)
zoom = input.getNumber(13)*10
end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0, 80, 0, 250) if nvis then screen.drawRect(1, 1, 11, 8) screen.drawTextBox(1, 2, 12, 8, "IR", 0, 0) end
screen.drawLine(w/2-5, h/2, w/2-10, h/2) screen.drawLine(w/2+5, h/2, w/2+10, h/2)
screen.drawLine(w/2, h/2-5, w/2, h/2-10) screen.drawLine(w/2, h/2+5, w/2, h/2+10)
screen.drawCircle(w/2, h/2, w/2.5) screen.drawTextBox(1, h-7, 32, 8, string.format("%.2f",zoom) .."X", -1, -1)
if stab then screen.drawRect(w-14, 1, 12, 8) screen.drawTextBox(w-13, 2, 12, 8, "ST", 0, 0) end
if laser then screen.drawRect(w-14, h-10, 12, 8) screen.drawTextBox(w-13, h-9, 12, 8, "LR", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(1, 1, w, 8, "X:" .. string.format("%.0f",lsrX) .. " Y:" .. string.format("%.0f",lsrZ), -1, -1) screen.drawTextBox(1, 8, w, 8, "ALT:" .. string.format("%.0f",lsrY), -1, -1) end
if lock then screen.drawRect(w-14, 1, 12, 8) screen.drawTextBox(w-13, 2, 12, 8, "LK", 0, 0) end
end
